        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0260",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "This project is continuously changing to optimize the functionality such as the "
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0261",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "search functionality"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0262",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0263",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "editor feature"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0264",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " (adding, removing, moving, and renaming items), and "
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0265",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "charts"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0266",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " as our data scientists keep improving on the accuracy of the data and determining what to show. I do believe that design is a constant iteration of improving the experience for the user.\n\n• "
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0267",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "(Worrying too much about the details.)"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0268",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " In a startup, there is only so much time and effort that you can invest. I made the mistake of worrying about the look of the UI. Taking a step back and communicating with the team helped me to reprioritize the important stuff.\n• "
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e0269",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "(Constant communication with the engineers.)"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8d73f7e7e02610",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " This helps to reduce any rework and having an understanding of the technical limitations will help strategize your designs. Sometimes, there will be some inaccuracy or missing components in the implementation, which is why it is best to explain the design handoffs before the implementation day."
          }
        ],
